I was once carefree in Lingnan

1048
00:44:27,030 --> 00:44:31,560
Only wishing
to return to the forest and dream

1049
00:44:31,760 --> 00:44:36,520
Enjoy the breeze
and the crescent moon again

1050
00:44:37,000 --> 00:44:41,400
Carefree and humble from then on

1051
00:44:41,880 --> 00:44:44,250
A little bit every day

1052
00:44:44,250 --> 00:44:46,650
A little bit crazier

1053
00:44:46,650 --> 00:44:48,990
A little bit every day

1054
00:44:48,990 --> 00:44:51,430
A day of insanity after another

1055
00:45:15,150 --> 00:45:18,280
I was once carefree in Lingnan

1056
00:45:19,200 --> 00:45:22,960
Swinging on green hills
and leafy branches

1057
00:45:24,000 --> 00:45:28,810
One day we'll meet in Chang'an

